    "The MLPs' dimensions for the standard structure are [64,128,256].",
    "Moreover, the Bi-LSTM hidden layer dimension is 128.The validation and testing protocol is meticulously designed to assess the solution's accuracy and robustness comprehensively.",
    "Testing involves processing motion data into non-overlapping 50 ms samples for 20 Hz tracking, with a pre-processing step of random sampling 1024 event points per sample.",
    "Initial tests without post-processing achieves 93% P10 accuracy, which is further enhanced through a novel confidence score mechanism, boosting the tracking accuracy to over 98% P10 accuracy.",
    "This mechanism accounts for the number of event points per sample, improving prediction reliability significantly.Results."
